<p>Photography class</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>A library</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>Saturday {morning}</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>A camera</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 80.8px;">
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>{French} cooking class</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>Anita kitchen</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>The {first} Tuesday every month</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>{money} to buy ingredients</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 61.2px;">
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>Beading class</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>A {golf} club</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center; border-color: #000000; border-width: 1.5px;">
<p>Wednesday</p>
