<p style="text-align: center;" data-start="116" data-end="180"> </p>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">PART 1: PRESTON COMMUNITY CENTRE CLASSES</strong></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Hello, this is Preston Community Centre.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Oh hello. My name is Andrew Shepherd. I’m ringing about the classes you offer.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Okay Mister Shepherd. Are there any classes in particular that you’re interested in?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Yes, you’ve got a class called Photography, I believe?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> That’s right. It’s the first time we offer this class because many people inquired about it last term. It’ll be held in a library, not far from our community center.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Right. I know it’s on the weekend, right?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Yes, it’s on Saturday, and it will occupy the whole <strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"59\">(1) morning</strong>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Okay, um… what do I need to bring?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Obviously, you have to bring your own camera. Some people bring a lot of accessories, like an extra lens, but there’s really no need for this class. It’s mainly focusing on composition really, and getting the most out of the basic camera.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> That’s exactly what I want. Okay then, I’ve heard there’s a class on cooking, right?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Yes, it’s called <strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"24\">(2) French</strong> Cooking class. As the name suggests, it will teach you cooking skills in French cuisine.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Oh great. Where will that be held?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> This class is special, so we arrange it in a kitchen where we can get the necessary cooking equipment. Let me see… yes, the Anita Kitchen. As for the time of the course, it used to be on the second Tuesday of every month, but there’s a small adjustment this time. Although it’s still held on a monthly basis, the exact time will be changed to the <strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"356\">(3) first</strong> Tuesday.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Well actually, it’s my wife who’s really interested, and I think it’s a good fit for her because our daughter has to take a guitar lesson every Tuesday, so my wife is available.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> That’s good. But I have to remind you that aprons are not provided in this class, so when you do come, please bring one with you in case you get dirty when cooking. What’s more, don’t forget to bring some <strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"212\">(4) money</strong> with you, as the ingredients for cooking, like vegetables or meat, have to be paid by yourself.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Okay, useful information to know. Then, there’s another class that my wife would like to join. That’s the beading class.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Oh, I’ve taken the class myself. The tutor is excellent. Last term it was held in a tennis club, which is going to be redecorated soon, so we plan to change this class to a <strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"180\">(5) golf</strong> club this time. And it’ll be held on the evening of every Wednesday.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Do I have to bring the beads with me?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Yes, that’s the only material needed for this class.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Okay, I think this class is also a good choice for her. Um, do you have any other classes that I can join?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> If you like, I think you can take our <strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"45\">(6) painting</strong> class. It’s a popular class, so this term we’re going to move it to a high school so that we can get more room.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> What time will it be?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> It’ll be on every Monday evening.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> The time’s good for me. Do I have to bring the paints?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Well, paints will be provided by the tutor. I know that… um, the information says you’ll just need some <strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"113\">(7) brushes</strong>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> I see.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"29\">\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">DETAILS OF BEADING CLASS (Questions 8–10)</strong></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Okay, just another question about the beading class. I’ve just remembered my wife asked me to find out the exact time. When will the first class begin?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Well, the deadline for registration is April the 30th, and we’re not going to start the class until <strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"107\">(8) 15 May</strong> (or May 15th).</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> OK. What’s the fee for this class?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> It was $95 last term, but the cost will be a little more this term. Well, let me check the details… okay, it’ll be $100 this term.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Just $5 more sounds reasonable. Then about the location… it’s in the club, which room exactly?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> Room <strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"12\">(9) J52</strong>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Okay, just one more question. Is parking convenient?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> I’m sorry to tell you that parking space is only available for the club’s premiere members. But if you drive, there’s a parking lot opposite the club, just beside the <strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"174\">(10) station</strong>. You need to pay only a small parking fee.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andrew:</strong> Okay, that’s all I want to know. I’ll call you later after I discuss it with my wife. Thank you very much.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Staff:</strong> You’re welcome. Bye bye.</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('659c3520-91da-4d20-8ba4-ae352d42eddc', 'e6213f11-b604-4534-b0c3-0b55b8775c40', 'checkbox', 'Questions 21–22', NULL, '<p>Choose <strong>TWO </strong>correct answers.</p>
<p>Which <strong>TWO</strong> topics were the aims of the geography lesson related to?</p>
', 'multiple_choice_many', 'null', '[{"option": "A global interdependency", "correct": true}, {"option": "B manufacturing method", "correct": false}, {"option": "C the environmental impact of trade", "correct": false}, {"option": "D transport systems", "correct": true}, {"option": "E the development of writing tools", "correct": false}]', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p><strong>Narrator:</strong> You will hear two trainee teachers called Dean and Hannah talking about their recent teaching practice in an elementary school. First you have some time to look at questions 21 to 24 on page five. Now listen carefully and answer questions 21 to 24.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Hi, Dean. Did you have a good weekend?</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> Yes, it was good to relax after a whole week of teaching practice. I really enjoyed the experience though.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Yes, so did I. And I think it went well. Anyway, are you okay to talk about the report we’ve got to write on the geography lesson we taught together? I was thinking we could make notes now and then divide the actual writing up between us.</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> Sure, good idea. Let’s begin with our lesson aim, shall we?</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Right. Well, I know the main one was getting the class to think about how people in different parts of the world are connected to each other through the things they buy and sell.</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> Yes, we took that from the syllabus for Grade 4. And then we decided to use pencils as our example, because they’re relatively simple in design and everyone’s used a pencil at some time or other. We should include that information too. Right?</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> And we also wanted to get the class thinking about how things are moved around the world in different ways—from the farms and the mines to the factories and then the stores.</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> That wasn’t in the core syllabus. I think we added that ourselves.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Yes, I think you’re right. (A – <strong>global interdependency</strong>; D – <strong>transport systems</strong>)</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> Okay then, the last section of the report contains a post-lesson analysis. We have to mention any problems we identified in our lesson when we taught it. So, any ideas?</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Well, I know we were really satisfied with our handouts and worksheets. We both thought they’d been at just the right level for the class. And I don’t know about you, but I think we worked well as a team.</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> Absolutely. Neither of us was too dominant, and we supported each other. Personally, the thing I think we didn’t get right was the way we paced things. Some things seemed to be rushed and others seemed to drag out too long. I don’t know how you feel about that.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Hmm, the same as you. If we did the same lesson again, I’d want to make some adjustments to that, but keep the same basic lesson plan. (E – <strong>the timing</strong>)</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> Okay, we see eye to eye on that. But there’s one other thing. At the time I seem to remember we both thought that organizing the children in sets of 6 didn’t work very well, and that pairs would have been better for certain tasks, so that the shy kids got more chance to contribute.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Yes, I remember that too, and we should put it into a report as well. (B – <strong>the student grouping</strong>)</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Narrator:</strong> Before you hear the rest of the discussion, you have some time to look at questions 25 to 30 on page six. Now listen and answer questions 25 to thirty.</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> Now, should we go over our lesson plan together before we write the report? It seems ages ago now.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Fine. Well, the whole lesson was based on the production and distribution of pencils. First we gave out the pencils and got the students to decide what they’re made of. Then when they’d come up with all five of the component materials, we talked about which countries produce most of these materials.</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> Oh yes, and we got volunteers to come to the front and mark the location of those on a map of the world. (25. Locate the top <strong>G producers</strong> on a world map) I remember they were really keen to volunteer. We had to stop them from calling the answers out loud!</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Right. Then we brainstormed all the different ways of getting goods from one place to another, and what the advantages and disadvantages of each one would be.</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> I remember one girl talking about using horses. (26. Discuss the pros and cons of different <strong>H methods of transport</strong>) That’s right. She seemed to be a bit stuck in the past. It was hard not to smile.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Yes. After that, we put them in small groups, and each group represented each of the countries on the map. They had to use their atlases to decide an itinerary for sending their raw materials to the USA, specifying the different ports and places on the way there. (27. In groups, discuss countries’ possible <strong>A export routes</strong> to the USA)</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> That’s right. And by the time they’d done that, it was break time. And after the break, they had to imagine they were pencil manufacturers in Chicago and fill in details on a <strong>(28) worksheet (E)</strong> about how they dispatch their pencils to different parts of the country.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> Oh yes. Okay. And then we had a class discussion about whether people will still be using pencils in 2050, and whether the design of pencils is likely to change. (29. Share ideas about the <strong>B future</strong> of pencils)</p>\n<p><strong>Hannah:</strong> And to round the lesson off, the kids had to spend 10 minutes planning a short <strong>(30) presentation (C talk)</strong> for another class about possible developments.</p>\n<p><strong>Dean:</strong> And that was it. Good. So I’ll write up that part and you…</p>\n<p><strong>Narrator:</strong> That is the end of Section 3. You now have half a minute to check your answers. Now turn to Section 4 on page 7.</p>\n"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('a9081caf-5c4e-47e5-8d65-cb171ad1efda', 'ee3f422e-fa1f-43d1-82bb-b39b5817fe7c', 'matrix', 'Questions 27 - 31', NULL, '<p>Reading Passage 3 has eight paragraphs, A-H.</p>
<p>Which paragraph contains the following information?</p>
', 'classification', 'null', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "simple", "legendTitle": null, "matrixItems": [{"itemText": "a summary of Franklin''s occupation in the period before his first expedition", "correctCategoryLetter": "A"}, {"itemText": "a reference to a feature of Franklin''s character in Nadolny''s novel that has no definite basis in fact", "correctCategoryLetter": "C"}, {"itemText": "a connection between the central theme of the novel and an environmental process", "correctCategoryLetter": "E"}, {"itemText": "a reference to the widespread appeal of Nadolny''s novel", "correctCategoryLetter": "H"}, {"itemText": "a summary of events following Franklin''s return from his first expedition", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}], "matrixCategories": [{"categoryText": "A", "categoryLetter": "A"}, {"categoryText": "B", "categoryLetter": "B"}, {"categoryText": "C", "categoryLetter": "C"}, {"categoryText": "D", "categoryLetter": "D"}, {"categoryText": "E", "categoryLetter": "E"}, {"categoryText": "F", "categoryLetter": "F"}, {"categoryText": "G", "categoryLetter": "G"}, {"categoryText": "H", "categoryLetter": "H"}]}', '[{"content": "<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">27. a summary of Franklin’s occupation in the period before his first expedition</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: A</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“John Franklin (1786-1847) <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"38\">joined the Navy at the age of 14, and fought at the battle of Trafalgar</strong>. When peace came, he turned his attention to Arctic exploration…”</em></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đoạn A tóm tắt các công việc của Franklin (gia nhập Hải quân, tham gia chiến trận) trước khi ông bắt đầu dẫn đầu chuyến thám hiểm Bắc Cực đầu tiên vào năm 1819.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">28. a reference to a feature of Franklin’s character in Nadolny’s novel that has no definite basis in fact</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"6\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"6,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: C</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“Nadolny has endowed John Franklin with a defining trait for which <strong data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"78\">there is no historical evidence: Langsamkeit (‘slowness’)</strong>.”</em></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"6,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Tác giả bài viết chỉ ra rằng đặc điểm “chậm chạp” mà tiểu thuyết gia Nadolny gán cho Franklin là điều <strong data-path-to-node=\"6,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"114\">không có bằng chứng lịch sử</strong> (<em data-path-to-node=\"6,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"143\">no historical evidence</em> tương ứng với <em data-path-to-node=\"6,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"180\">no definite basis in fact</em>).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">29. a connection between the central theme of the novel and an environmental process</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"9\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: E</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"12\">Ice is a slow mover</strong>… crystals… thickens… consolidates into young ice… deepens to become pack ice. Ice demands a corresponding patience…”</em></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Chủ đề trung tâm của tiểu thuyết là “sự chậm chạp”. Đoạn E kết nối chủ đề này với <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"94\">quá trình hình thành băng</strong> — một hiện tượng môi trường diễn ra từ tốn, đòi hỏi sự kiên nhẫn từ con người.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">30. a reference to the widespread appeal of Nadolny’s novel</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"12\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: H</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“Since it was first published… has <strong data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"48\">sold more than a million copies and been translated into 15 languages</strong>. It has been adopted as a manual and manifesto by European pressure groups…”</em></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"12,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đoạn H nói về sự thành công vang dội và sức ảnh hưởng rộng khắp (<em data-path-to-node=\"12,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"77\">widespread appeal</em>) của cuốn sách, từ doanh số kỷ lục đến việc được các tổ chức chính trị, xã hội đón nhận.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">31. a summary of events following Franklin’s return from his first expedition</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"15\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án: B</strong></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"11\">“There followed a <strong data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"29\">career as a travel writer and public speaker</strong>… Then in 1845, Franklin set off back to the Arctic…”</em></li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Sau chuyến đi đầu tiên (kết thúc ở đoạn A), đoạn B tóm tắt những gì Franklin làm sau khi trở về (viết sách, diễn thuyết) và kể về chuyến thám hiểm cuối cùng thảm khốc của ông.</li>\n</ul>\n"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('b812e86c-c7ee-4e4e-860b-d67f0f2e9b9e', '7aadd5b2-a63b-4b58-9c43-bd16f49a1669', 'matching', 'Questions 27–30', NULL, '<p>What comment is made about the programme for each of the following shows?</p>
<p>Choose FOUR answers from the box and write the correct letter, A–F, next to Questions 27–30.</p>
', 'matching_features', NULL, '[{"option": "A", "correct": false}, {"option": "B", "correct": false}, {"option": "C", "correct": false}, {"option": "D", "correct": false}, {"option": "E", "correct": false}, {"option": "F", "correct": false}]', '{"layoutType": "summary", "summaryText": "<p><strong>Shows</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Ruy Blas {It resembles an artwork.}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Man of La Mancha {It contains insights into the show.}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The Tragedy of Jane Shore {It is historically significant for a country.}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The Sailors’ Festival {It is included in a recent project.}</p>", "answerOptions": [{"optionText": "Its origin is somewhat controversial."}, {"optionText": "It is historically significant for a country."}, {"optionText": "It was effective at attracting audiences."}, {"optionText": "It is included in a recent project."}, {"optionText": "It contains insights into the show."}, {"optionText": "It resembles an artwork."}], "matchingItems": [{"questionPart": "Ruy Blas", "correctAnswer": "It resembles an artwork.", "sectionContent": null}, {"questionPart": "Man of La Mancha", "correctAnswer": "It contains insights into the show.", "sectionContent": null}, {"questionPart": "The Tragedy of Jane Shore", "correctAnswer": "It is historically significant for a country.", "sectionContent": null}, {"questionPart": "The Sailors’ Festival", "correctAnswer": "It is included in a recent project.", "sectionContent": null}]}', '{"layoutType": "standard", "legendTitle": null, "matrixItems": null, "matrixCategories": null}', '[{"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}, {"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}, {"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}, {"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('8a6e711a-dd44-4f72-b84e-ecbe00d28531', 'd61d12be-174b-4c2d-a503-c97f6ab88597', 'matrix', 'Questions 17–20', NULL, '<p>Label the map below.<br />Drag the correct letter, A–G, next to Questions 17–20.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64,"></p>
', 'other', NULL, '[{"option": "A", "correct": false}, {"option": "B", "correct": false}, {"option": "C", "correct": false}, {"option": "D", "correct": false}, {"option": "E", "correct": false}, {"option": "F", "correct": false}, {"option": "G", "correct": false}]', '{"layoutType": "standard", "summaryText": null, "answerOptions": null, "matchingItems": null}', '{"layoutType": "simple", "legendTitle": null, "matrixItems": [{"itemText": "bridge foundations", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}, {"itemText": "rubbish pit", "correctCategoryLetter": "A"}, {"itemText": "meeting hall", "correctCategoryLetter": "G"}, {"itemText": "fish pond", "correctCategoryLetter": "E"}], "matrixCategories": [{"categoryText": "A", "categoryLetter": "A"}, {"categoryText": "B", "categoryLetter": "B"}, {"categoryText": "C", "categoryLetter": "C"}, {"categoryText": "D", "categoryLetter": "D"}, {"categoryText": "E", "categoryLetter": "E"}, {"categoryText": "F", "categoryLetter": "F"}, {"categoryText": "G", "categoryLetter": "G"}]}', '[{"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}, {"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}, {"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}, {"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('84292d5d-f704-4bae-9698-b173ee017c72', '550c6993-3ef0-4f71-9d5c-7d38a7389ba1', 'fillup', 'Questions 21-22', '<p>Write <strong>NO MORE THAN THREE WORDS</strong> for each answer.</p>
<p>Reasons for having study Syndicates:</p>
<p>Teaching one another is a good way to learn</p>
<p>It gives the opportunity to {Share ideas}</p>
<p>Shared reading means fuller notes</p>
<p>You can do {Much deeper research}</p>
', NULL, 'gap_filling', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h2 data-path-to-node=\"2\">PART 3</h2>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> Right then, are we ready Bob, Helen?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Uh, yeah.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> And is someone taking notes for John? He’s at a tutorial isn’t he?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> Yeah, I’ll let him know what we agree. Good, okay. Well, first thing is, has anyone apart from me actually been in a study syndicate before?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob/Helen:</strong> No.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> What does it actually involve, Andy?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> Well, the idea is that it’s a way for us, for students, to study together without a teacher. When I did it last time I found it helpful because, well as I said, there’s no teacher, so it means we’re teaching one another and I found I really learnt a lot through having to teach it myself. It seemed a very good way to learn.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> And presumably it gives us the chance to <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"46\">(21) share ideas</strong></span> as well.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> And you get fuller notes if you’re all doing the reading.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> That’s right, and as well as that, because of that really, you can do, you know, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"87\">(22) much deeper research</strong></span>. So I thought we could try it to revise what we’ve done on the geology course, cause I know this is the one that most of us are worried about—the geology exam.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Alright, yes. So the idea is we all look at a different topic, um, a different topic from the geology course and then give a presentation and talk about it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> That’s right. I’ve drawn up the framework of a table which might be useful here. I’ve made a copy.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> Oh, thanks.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> For the first topic, I thought we could maybe do <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"55\">(23) mountain building</strong>.</span> Is that alright?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Yeah, sure. Actually, would you mind if I did that? I’m quite interested in it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> Right, right. So is May 9th okay for that?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Uh-huh, yeah. I’ll just write that down: May 9th, Bob, Mountain Building.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> And the following week, it can’t be May 16th because of our tutorial, but what about the<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> <span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"95\">(24) 17th May</strong> (hoặc <strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"115\">May 17th</strong>)?</span></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Hmm, okay.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> And what about the next topic? What would be the next priority?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> Well, there’s glaciated areas, but I don’t want to do that.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> Fair enough. Actually, I don’t mind having a bash. I did an assignment on them. So, Glaciated areas, Andy. Then we need someone to do rock formation.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> Yeah, okay. And John said he’d like to too. So you can put us both down for that. When?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> May 23rd would be best. Rock formation, Helen and John. Right, that really only leaves one week before the exams. Shall we make it on the 30th?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Uh, I can’t make it, I’m afraid. <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"38\">(25) 29th May</strong> (hoặc <strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"58\">May 29th</strong>)</span>? The exam’s on June 3rd, it’ll have to be.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> OK. Any ideas for a topic?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> Uh, John said he wouldn’t mind doing something on volcanoes.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> Great, that’s everyone then.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"31\" />\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> And um, how long should these presentations be?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Well, it’s obviously up to us. In my experience, 30 minutes is about enough.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> Hmm, maybe a bit short. I’d have thought 40 minutes would be more like it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> Well, should we say <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"26\">(26) 30–40 minutes</strong></span>?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> Okay, and presumably time for <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"37\">(27) questions and discussion</strong> ?</span></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> Yes, together they usually take about 20 minutes. Where should we get the information from? Is it mainly lecture notes?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Well actually, I suggest we avoid those because we already have all that information. I think it’s better to go more deeply. We could use the bibliography and anything else we find in the library.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> Any other books? Hmm, and articles, you know, from the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"62\">(28) journals</strong> (hoặc <strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"82\">journal</strong>).</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> And then of course there’s lots of stuff on the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"54\">(29) internet</strong>.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"41\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"41\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Yes, that’s the sort of thing.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"42\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"42\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Andy:</strong> And what about the presentations? Will we just be talking?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"43\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"43\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Bob:</strong> Uh, presumably we can’t use slides, it’d be a bit difficult. But uh, we can use the OHP (Overhead Projector) and the whiteboard of course. And we can make <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"43\" data-index-in-node=\"160\">(30) photocopy </strong></span>of our notes so everyone can have a copy.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"44\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"44\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Helen:</strong> Yes, great. So is there anything else?</p>\n"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('36439653-639c-41ec-8161-ccb05daab76c', 'ee3f422e-fa1f-43d1-82bb-b39b5817fe7c', 'matching', 'Questions 32 - 35', NULL, '<p>Complete the summary using the list of words, <strong>A-L</strong>, below.</p>
<p>Write the correct letter, <strong>A-L</strong>, in boxes 32-35 on your answer sheet.</p>', 'matching_features', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "summary", "summaryText": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>John Franklin and the Quality of Slowness</strong></p>\n<p>Little is known from Franklin''s correspondence and published writings about his {G personality} . The author, Nadolny, suggests that Franklin''s whole life can be explained by the quality of ''slowness'' . He begins the book by showing how this affects the young Franklin''s {K sporting} activities, and makes him become {F an outsider} . As a child, it is the quality of {L timelessness} that attracts Franklin to the Arctic.</p>", "answerOptions": [{"optionText": "A a bully"}, {"optionText": "B discoveries"}, {"optionText": "C educational"}, {"optionText": "D family"}, {"optionText": "E isolation"}, {"optionText": "F an outsider"}, {"optionText": "G personality"}, {"optionText": "H problems"}, {"optionText": "I remoteness"}, {"optionText": "J a scholar"}, {"optionText": "K sporting"}, {"optionText": "L timelessness"}], "matchingItems": null}', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"2\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">32. {G} personality</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án:</strong> <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">G. personality</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn C cho biết Franklin là người: “…who kept <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"59\">introspection and self-analysis</strong> to a minimum.”</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Vì Franklin luôn giữ việc tự phân tích bản thân ở mức tối thiểu trong các ghi chép cá nhân, nên chúng ta biết rất ít về <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"132\">nhân cách/đời sống nội tâm</strong> (<strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"160\">personality</strong>) thực sự của ông.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">33. {K} sporting</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"5\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án:</strong> <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">K. sporting</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn D mô tả cảnh mở đầu cuốn sách khi Franklin còn nhỏ: “…failing to <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"83\">catch a ball</strong> because his reaction time is too slow.”</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Việc “bắt bóng” là một hoạt động <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"45\">thể thao/thể chất</strong> (<strong data-path-to-node=\"5,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"64\">sporting</strong>). Sự chậm chạp đã ảnh hưởng trực tiếp đến khả năng này của ông.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">34. {F} an outsider</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"7\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án:</strong> <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">F. an outsider</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn D đề cập: “Despite the <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"39\">bullying of his peers</strong>, Franklin resolves <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"80\">not to fall into step</strong> with ‘their way of doing things’.”</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Vì không theo kịp tốc độ của bạn bè và bị bắt nạt, Franklin đã chọn cách không hòa nhập, khiến ông trở thành một <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"125\">người ngoài cuộc</strong> (<strong data-path-to-node=\"7,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"143\">an outsider</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">35. {L} timelessness</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"9\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Đáp án:</strong> <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">L. timelessness</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> Đoạn D mô tả mong ước của cậu bé Franklin: “…dreaming of the <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"74\">‘time without hours and days’</strong> which exists in the far north…”</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Franklin bị thu hút bởi Bắc Cực vì đó là nơi có khái niệm “thời gian không có giờ và ngày”, tương ứng với sự <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"121\">vô tận/không thời gian</strong> (<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"145\">timelessness</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('5fca331d-07ea-427f-9ddf-bfa353ac5652', '983125ba-0dc7-48ed-b003-bf463a32a0b4', 'fillup', 'Questions 1–4', '<div class="quests-inner-desc">
<div class="txt">
<p><em>Complete the table below.</em></p>
<p><em>Write </em><strong><em>ONE WORD ONLY</em></strong><em> for each answer.</em></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">
</div>
</div>
<div class="quests-des">
<div class="content-write">
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><strong>SCHOOL ART COMPETITION</strong></p>
<div class="quill-better-table-wrapper">
<div class="choice-table-wrap">
<table class="quill-better-table choice-table" style="width: 94.674%; border-collapse: collapse; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" border="1">
<colgroup>
<col class="ql-align-center" style="width: 19.913%;" width="132" />
<col class="ql-align-center" style="width: 32.7358%;" width="217" />
<col class="ql-align-center" style="width: 18.5553%;" width="123" />
<col class="ql-align-center" style="width: 28.8136%;" width="191" /></colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-row="1">
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="4" rowspan="1" data-row="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;" data-row="1" data-cell="1" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)"><strong>Arrangements for this year</strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-row="2">
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="2" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="2" data-cell="1" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)"><strong>Age group</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="2" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="2" data-cell="2" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)"><strong>Theme</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="2" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="2" data-cell="3" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)"><strong>Type of art</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="2" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="2" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(242, 242, 242)"><strong>Prize</strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-row="3">
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="3" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="1" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">Junior students</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="3" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="2" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span class="fill-history-correct">{animals}</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="3" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="3" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">a drawing</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="3" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">{zoo}</p>
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="3" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">tickets</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-row="4">
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="1" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">Senior students</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="2" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">the {city}</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="3" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">a photograph</p>
</td>
<td style="border-color: #000000;" colspan="1" rowspan="1" data-row="4" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">a {travel}</p>
<p class="qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center" data-row="4" data-cell="4" data-rowspan="1" data-colspan="1" data-cell-bg="rgb(255, 255, 255)">voucher</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
', NULL, 'gap_filling', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h2 data-path-to-node=\"2\">PART 1</h2>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Hi John.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Hi Wendy, thanks for coming to discuss the school art competition. I know this is your first year organizing it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Well I’ve got some ideas, but I’d appreciate some help with arrangements.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> OK. We usually divide the competition into age groups. The first age group is junior students.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> I’ll just note that down.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Last year we went with a theme of family. That worked very well.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Yes, something simple is best for young children I think. How about <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"75\">(1) animals</strong></span> this year?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Sounds good.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> And for the type of art, last year children in the junior age group created a drawing. Shall we stick with that?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Yes and for the prize, I heard last year we gave cinema tickets to the winner. Is that right?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Yes but you know, it might be nice to give the winners tickets to the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"77\">(2) zoo</strong></span> this time.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Good idea, okay.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Finally for the senior students, we also have to think of a theme. I’ve got a couple of ideas. One is the future.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Hmm. I’m not quite sure how students might approach that theme. It could be tricky.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Um, my other idea was the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"33\">(3) city</strong></span>. What do you think?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Good. Students could get some really interesting images with that theme. And for the type of art, I think a photograph would work well.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Great idea. And as a prize, one of our sponsors is willing to donate a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"78\">(4) travel</strong></span> voucher that the winner can spend.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Fantastic! They can find inspiration for their next artworks.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"21\" />\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Now let’s discuss some further details of the competition.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Sure.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> First of all, the deadline for submitting artwork. We want to award the prizes on May the 25th. Last year we needed a week to judge the winners and finalize arrangements for the awards night. How about if entrants submit their artwork by <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"244\">(5) 18th May</strong></span>?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Sure. I’ll just note that down. Where should they submit their artworks? At the office?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Actually there’s more space at the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"41\">(6) library</strong></span>, so let’s ask students to take their art there.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Okay. In terms of judging the competition, what did you do last year?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> We used an excellent local artist. We should try and use her again this year. Her name is Rebecca Lee.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Okay. Is that L-double-E?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> No it’s <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"14\">(7) L-E-I-G-H</strong></span>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Right. I guess I should also note down her number so that I can get in contact with her after we finalize the rest of the competition details.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Sure, I’ve got her number here. Are you ready? It’s <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"58\">(8) 04076254633</strong></span>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Got it. After the judging, where are we going to display the artworks?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> How about we book the Bridge Street Gallery? It’s a beautiful old building.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> It is. So can you go ahead and book it?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Yes. And do you think we should also publish the artworks in the school <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"78\">(9) magazine</strong></span>?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> Yes definitely. I think the winning students would be delighted to see that.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Great. Now in terms of the art exhibition of the students’ work, should we make it a morning event and follow it up with a special lunch or afternoon tea for parents?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wendy:</strong> I was thinking a late afternoon event might be better so that parents can attend after work. After the exhibition, we could put on a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"140\">(10) dinner</strong></span>. What do you think?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">John:</strong> Yes, that could be nice. Now I wanted…</p>\n"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('692465b1-e2c1-4c1b-9296-be58eceb980a', '9dc07e7a-357d-4148-a5c9-bebf94577384', 'radio', 'Questions 1–5', NULL, '<p>Choose <strong>TRUE </strong>if the statement agrees with the information given in the text, choose <strong>FALSE </strong>if the statement contradicts the information, or choose <strong>NOT GIVEN </strong>if there is no information on this.</p>
', 'multiple_choice_single', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"content": "TRUE"}, {"content": "FALSE"}, {"content": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "Donald Johanson was uncertain about the nature of the elbow bone he found in Afar."}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"content": "TRUE"}, {"content": "FALSE"}, {"content": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": " Several bones were found by Donald Johanson at the same site in Afar."}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"content": "TRUE"}, {"content": "FALSE"}, {"content": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "The experts realised the importance of the discovery at Afar."}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"content": "TRUE"}, {"content": "FALSE"}, {"content": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "It was the upper part of the skeleton that had suffered the least damage."}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"content": "TRUE"}, {"content": "FALSE"}, {"content": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "The skeleton’s measurements helped Johanson’s team to decide if it was male or female."}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"1\">Câu 1: FALSE</p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"2\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Vị trí:</strong> Đoạn 1, dòng 6-7.</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"2,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “Straight away, he recognized it as coming from the elbow of a human ancestor.”</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Tác giả dùng cụm từ <strong data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"32\">“Straight away”</strong> (Ngay lập tức) để khẳng định việc Donald Johanson nhận ra mảnh xương khuỷu tay. Điều này trái ngược hoàn toàn với từ <strong data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"165\">“uncertain”</strong> (không chắc chắn) trong câu hỏi.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\">Câu 2: TRUE</p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"4\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Vị trí:</strong> Đoạn 1, dòng 8-9.</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “I saw bits of the skull, a chunk of jaw, a couple of vertebrae…”</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"4,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Johanson liệt kê một loạt các phần xương khác nhau được tìm thấy tại cùng một địa điểm (mảnh hộp sọ, xương hàm, đốt sống). Vì vậy, thông tin tìm thấy <strong data-path-to-node=\"4,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"162\">“nhiều mảnh xương”</strong> (several bones) là chính xác.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Câu 3: TRUE</p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"6\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"6,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Vị trí:</strong> Đoạn 2, dòng 1-2.</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “It was immediately obvious that the skeleton was a significant find…”</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"6,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Cụm từ <strong data-path-to-node=\"6,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"19\">“significant find”</strong> (phát hiện quan trọng) chính là cách viết khác của <strong data-path-to-node=\"6,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"89\">“importance of the discovery”</strong>. Bài đọc khẳng định tầm quan trọng này là “hiển nhiên ngay lập tức” (immediately obvious) đối với các chuyên gia.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\">Câu 4: NOT GIVEN</p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"8\">\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Vị trí:</strong> Đoạn 2, dòng 4-5.</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “…it was also the most complete – 40% of the skeleton had been preserved.”</li>\n<li><strong data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Bài đọc chỉ cung cấp con số 40% bộ xương được bảo tồn. Tác giả <strong data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"75\">không hề cung cấp thông tin hay so sánh</strong> xem phần phía trên (upper part) bị hư hại nhiều hay ít hơn các phần khác, nên thông tin này không có trong bài.</li>\n</ul>\n"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('6160b489-003e-4cb1-aa54-f58d8bd998ab', 'a1014b92-453c-4cbd-888d-a6612e8c6c98', 'matching', 'Questions 32–35', NULL, '<p>Complete the summary using the list of words and phrases, <strong>A–I</strong>, below.</p>
<p>Write the correct letter, <strong>A–I</strong>, in boxes 32–35 on your answer sheet.</p>
', 'matching_features', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "summary", "summaryText": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Theories about Mahy’s style</strong></span></p>\n<p>Mahy’s determination to earn a living from writing has encouraged her to find the ideas for her work in {B everyday} places. The stories themselves are set in locations that are {E exotic and ordinary} . In terms of characterisation, almost all of her books feature unruly people, and very often an adolescent who possesses {I magical} abilities. Finally, the endings of the stories tend to be {H unsurprising but satisfying} .</p>", "answerOptions": [{"optionText": "A disruptive and unpredictable"}, {"optionText": "B everyday"}, {"optionText": "C loveable"}, {"optionText": "D controversial"}, {"optionText": "E exotic and ordinary"}, {"optionText": "F isolated"}, {"optionText": "G unconfident"}, {"optionText": "H unsurprising but satisfying"}, {"optionText": "I magical"}], "matchingItems": null}', 'null', '[{"content": "<p><strong>32. Mahy’s determination to earn a living from writing has encouraged her to find the ideas for her work in B. everyday places.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"16\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án:</strong> <strong>B (everyday)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dẫn chứng:</strong> (Đoạn 2) “…it has been a matter of going out and finding inspiration from <strong>her immediate environment</strong>: the writing on the side of a bus; a spelling mistake in a note to herself…”</li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> “Immediate environment” (môi trường xung quanh trực tiếp) và các ví dụ (xe buýt, lỗi chính tả) cho thấy bà lấy ý tưởng từ những nơi <strong>hàng ngày</strong> (<strong>everyday</strong>).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>33. The stories themselves are set in locations that are  E. exotic and ordinary.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"18\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án:</strong> <strong>E (exotic and ordinary)</strong></li>\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation-7\">Dẫn chứng:</span></strong><span class=\"citation-7\"> (Đoạn 2) “…the settings for her stories are delightfully varied, as these books celebrate the dramatic plot twists and unpredictability of adventures on the </span><strong><span class=\"citation-7\">high seas or in Antarctica</span></strong><span class=\"citation-7\">, and also in quite </span><strong><span class=\"citation-7\">unassuming places like the library or even down the back of a chair at home</span></strong><span class=\"citation-7 citation-end-7\">.”</span></li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> Các địa điểm bao gồm những nơi xa lạ (high seas/Antarctica – <strong>exotic</strong>) và những nơi quen thuộc (library/back of a chair – <strong>ordinary</strong>).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>34. …and very often an adolescent who possesses  I. magical abilities.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"20\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án:</strong> <strong>I (magical)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dẫn chứng:</strong> (Đoạn 3) “Her fictions often have at their heart a young adult burdened with <strong>special powers, such as the ability to cast spells</strong>…”</li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> “Special powers” và khả năng “cast spells” (yểm bùa) là những khả năng <strong>phép thuật</strong> (<strong>magical</strong>).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>35. Finally, the endings of the stories tend to be H. unsurprising but satisfying.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"22\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án:</strong> <strong>H (unsurprising but satisfying)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dẫn chứng:</strong> (Đoạn 3) “…while the conclusions of her tales are usually <strong>predictable</strong>, they leave the reader feeling <strong>absolutely complete</strong>…”</li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> “Predictable” đồng nghĩa với <strong>unsurprising</strong>, và “absolutely complete” đồng nghĩa với <strong>satisfying</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('fbdd4811-eead-4ed0-b7d3-29beefde978c', '1309e07e-3d9f-487e-a665-b3c72c540cc1', 'checkbox', 'Questions 25-26', NULL, '<p>Choose <strong>TWO </strong>letters, A–E.</p>
<p>25 – 26 Which <strong>TWO </strong>recommendations for getting out of a cycle of procrastination does the writer give?</p>
', 'multiple_choice_many', '[{"correct": null, "options": [{"content": null}], "question": null}]', '[{"option": "A. not judging ourselves harshly", "correct": true}, {"option": "B. setting ourselves manageable aims", "correct": false}, {"option": "C. rewarding ourselves for tasks achieved", "correct": false}, {"option": "D. prioritising tasks according to their importance", "correct": false}, {"option": "E. avoiding things that stop us concentrating on our tasks", "correct": true}]', '{"layoutType": ["standard"], "summaryText": null, "answerOptions": null, "matchingItems": null}', '{"layoutType": ["standard"], "legendTitle": null, "matrixItems": null, "matrixCategories": null}', '[{"content": "<p>25–26. A, E<br />(Đoạn F: “Forgiving ourselves and feeling compassion when we procrastinate can help break the procrastination cycle… fend off distractions that can occupy our minds.”)<br />→ Hai lời khuyên của tác giả để thoát khỏi vòng lặp trì hoãn là:</p>\n<p>A: Không tự trách bản thân quá mức (not judging ourselves harshly).<br />E: Tránh những thứ làm xao nhãng, khiến ta không tập trung (avoiding things that stop us concentrating).<br /> <br /> <br /> </p>\n"}]', 3);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('3d1d62d7-c224-4249-b2c4-989bb7faaaab', 'a1014b92-453c-4cbd-888d-a6612e8c6c98', 'radio', 'Questions 36-40', NULL, '<p>Choose the correct letter, A, B, C or D.</p>
', 'multiple-choice', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"content": "A. It is partly based on true history."}, {"content": "B. It was restructured in the writing process."}, {"content": "C. It is quite different from conventional fantasy."}, {"content": "D. It does not reflect the usual themes in Mahy’s work."}], "question": "What does the writer say about The Magician of Hoad?"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"content": "A. was first illustrated in 1991."}, {"content": "B. is written in plain language."}, {"content": "C. is an old favourite for many families."}, {"content": "D. has not been read aloud by Mahy."}], "question": "According to the writer, Bubble Trouble"}, {"correct": 3, "options": [{"content": "A. show how Mahy''s style has changed."}, {"content": "B. criticise Mahy''s children''s stories."}, {"content": "C. describe how new media have changed reading."}, {"content": "D. illustrate Mahy''s popularity with different generations."}], "question": "The writer''s purpose in the fifth paragraph is to"}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"content": "A. Readers sometimes do not finish Mahy’s books."}, {"content": "B. Mahy actively encourages feedback from readers."}, {"content": "C. Readers are necessary in order to complete a book."}, {"content": "D. Mahy does not realise how important readers are."}], "question": "According to the sixth paragraph, which of the following is true?"}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"content": "A. comparing Mahy’s writing to David Hill’s"}, {"content": "B. giving an example of Mahy’s influence"}, {"content": "C. explaining why Mahy’s language is humorous"}, {"content": "D. criticising the way Mahy plays with words"}], "question": "What is the writer doing in the final paragraph?"}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p><strong>36. What does the writer say about <em>The Magician of Hoad</em>?</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"26\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án: B. It was restructured in the writing process.</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dẫn chứng:</strong> (Đoạn 4) “The story ballooned at one point to 800 pages and has been through <strong>at least two substantial rewrites</strong>.”</li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> Việc trải qua nhiều lần viết lại đáng kể (“substantial rewrites”) cho thấy cuốn sách đã được <strong>tái cấu trúc</strong> (<strong>restructured</strong>).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>37. According to the writer, <em>Bubble Trouble</em></strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"28\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án: C. is an old favourite for many families.</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dẫn chứng:</strong> (Đoạn 5) “<strong>Perhaps more than any other work, <em>Bubble Trouble</em> is the Mahy that New Zealand children and their parents know so well</strong>…”</li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> Việc được nhiều gia đình biết rõ chứng tỏ nó là một tác phẩm được yêu thích từ lâu (<strong>old favourite</strong>).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>38. The writer’s purpose in the fifth paragraph is to</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"30\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án: D. illustrate Mahy’s popularity with different generations.</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dẫn chứng:</strong> (Đoạn 6) Tác giả liệt kê các tác phẩm của Mahy được đọc qua các thập kỷ khác nhau: “late 1960s” (tác giả đọc), “1970s” (con gái riêng của tác giả), “80s and 90s” (con của tác giả), “21st century” (cháu của tác giả).</li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> Việc này cho thấy sự nổi tiếng <strong>liên tục</strong> và <strong>kéo dài qua nhiều thế hệ</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>39. According to the sixth paragraph, which of the following is true?</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"32\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án: C. Readers are necessary in order to complete a book.</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dẫn chứng:</strong> (Đoạn 7) “a book is not properly finished, she has often said, <strong>until it has been read, because a reader brings something important to the book</strong>.”</li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> Quan điểm của Mahy là cuốn sách chưa hoàn thành cho đến khi có người đọc.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>40. What is the writer doing in the final paragraph?</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"34\">\n<li><strong>Đáp án: B. giving an example of Mahy’s influence</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dẫn chứng:</strong> (Đoạn 9) Tác giả kể lại câu chuyện của David Hill, một nhà văn khác, người đã bị <strong>ảnh hưởng</strong> (<em>“affected by her peculiarly alert way of looking at the world”</em>) bởi cách Mahy nhìn thế giới và chơi chữ.</li>\n<li><strong>Giải thích:</strong> Câu chuyện của Hill là một bằng chứng rõ ràng về <strong>tầm ảnh hưởng</strong> của Mahy đối với các nhà văn khác.</li>\n</ul>\n"}]', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('7b8c7aa2-176d-43f0-97ca-f501460b2b7e', '494be70d-a584-468a-8dd3-63948f15aab7', 'fillup', 'Question 1-10', '<p>Complete the form below.</p>
<p>Write <strong>ONE WORD AND/OR NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</p>
<table class="MsoNormalTable" style="border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed; border: none; mso-yfti-tbllook: 1536; mso-padding-alt: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt; mso-border-insideh: cell-none; mso-border-insidev: cell-none;" border="1" width="602" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tbody>
<tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes; height: 26.25pt;">
<td style="width: 451.25pt; border: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: solid #DDDDDD .75pt; padding: 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt; height: 26.25pt;" width="602"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Superior Home Appliances – Customer Complaint Form</span></strong></span></td>
</tr>
<tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 1; height: 53.25pt;">
<td style="width: 451.25pt; border: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid #DDDDDD .75pt; mso-border-alt: solid #DDDDDD .75pt; padding: 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt; height: 53.25pt;" width="602">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Example</span></em></strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Type of appliance: <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><u>fridge</u></em></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 2; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes; height: 369.75pt;">
<td style="width: 451.25pt; border: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid #DDDDDD .75pt; mso-border-alt: solid #DDDDDD .75pt; padding: 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt; height: 369.75pt;" width="602">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Name: Jessica Brown</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Tel: 5823 2210</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Under warranty: yes</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Model type: a {top}</span><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;"> mount</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Model number: S 654 391 X</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Colour: {silver}</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Date of purchase: {12th January|12 Janurary}</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">Problems: ∙ the {alarm} </span></span><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">in the fridge sounded</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">∙ freezer temperature is {10} </span></span><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">degrees</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">∙ main fridge not working.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Nearest service centre: Ken’s Appliances (near the {station} </span><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">Comments</span><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;">:</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">∙ customer needs the fridge to store food for her {sandwich}</span></span><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;"> shop</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">∙ value of food in fridge</span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;"> {180}</span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">: $ 8</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">To do: </span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">∙ get the {manager}</span></span><span lang="vi" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #15191e;"> to call her today</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Gungsuh; color: #15191e;">∙ replace damaged {door}</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>', NULL, 'gap_filling', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">SECTION 1: <span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Superior Home Appliances</span></strong></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">(Example)</strong> <strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"10\">Ian:</strong> Hello Superior Home Appliances, this is Ian here.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"65\">Jessica:</strong> Oh hello. Yes, I have a new fridge and I’m ringing to report a fault with it. I need you to send someone out to have a look at it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> OK, I’ll fill in a customer complaint form and arrange for one of our repair agents to come out to you. Now, can I just get some contact details from you for the form? Your name is Jessica?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Jessica Brown.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Okay. And if I can just get a contact telephone number?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Our home phone number is <strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"34\">5823 2210</strong>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Got it. Now, can I get some more details about the fridge?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Well, it’s been playing up since yesterday afternoon.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> I see. And is it still under warranty?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Well I should think so, it’s only a couple of weeks old.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> That’s fine then. Now I just need to get some more information about the make and model. Is it a top mount, a bottom mount, or a side by side?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> The freezer is on <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">(1) top</strong></span>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> And have you got the model number there?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Yes, it’s here on the instructions booklet. It’s <strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"58\">S 654 391 X</strong>.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> OK. So it’s <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"17\">(2) silver</strong></span> in colour?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> That’s right. I thought it was so much nicer than the usual white ones.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Hmm. Now if I could just get a few details from you first. When did you buy the fridge?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Well, as I said, it was only a few weeks ago, but I don’t have the receipt in front of me at the moment. I do know that it was delivered on the 6th of February.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Okay well, I can use that date to search on the computer. Hmm… ah, here it is. It says here you bought it on <span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"116\">(3</strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"116\">) </strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"116\">12th</strong></span> <span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"116\">January </strong></span></span>(hoặc 12th January).</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Now, what exactly is wrong with the fridge?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Well, my fridge is fitted with an <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"43\">(4) alarm</strong></span> and it started to go off. It made an awful noise.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> So what was wrong?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Well, when I went to check the freezer, it felt pretty warm. It’s <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"75\">(5) 10</strong></span> degrees and it should be minus 18. So everything is melting, and then the main part of the fridge doesn’t seem to be working either.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Hmm, I see. I’ve made a note of that on the form and I’ll pass it on to the service agent.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> When can they come and fix it?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Let’s find the closest one to you. Um, let’s see… that’s Ken’s Appliances and they’ve got two centres in your area. One near the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"136\">(6) station</strong></span> and another one in the shopping centre.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Well, we’re miles away from the shopping centre, so the station one would be closer.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> I’ll ring them in a minute, but I should warn you it could take a day or two for them to get to you.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> What?! What am I going to do without a fridge? Look, there’s a fridge full of food there and it’s all going off. I’ll have to throw it all out, you know.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Yes, I do sympathize.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> It’s not just that, this is going to affect my business. I run a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"74\">(7) sandwich</strong></span> shop and that’s where I keep my stock.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Hmm, I see. Look Jessica, if you tell me how much the stock is worth, we can send you a cheque for that amount, though there is a maximum of $250.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Well, I’ve just filled it with <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"40\">(8) 180</strong></span> dollars worth of meat and salad, so that would be something I suppose. But how long is my business expected to survive without a fridge? It’s just not good enough.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Yes, I understand your concerns, but that’s all I can really offer you.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"37\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"37\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Well, I’d like to speak to someone higher up about this.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"38\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> Um, I can ask my <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"38\" data-index-in-node=\"22\">(9) manager</strong></span> to ring you back by close of business today. Would that be acceptable?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"39\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"39\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Yes, thank you.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"40\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"40\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> I do apologize for all the inconvenience. Is there anything else I can help you with?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"41\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"41\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Jessica:</strong> Actually, there is one more thing. The<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> <span style=\"background-color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"41\" data-index-in-node=\"48\">(10) door</strong></span></span> has a dent in it on the left-hand side. It wasn’t there in the shop, so it must have happened when it was delivered. I’d like that replaced too.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"42\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"42\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Ian:</strong> I’ll make a note of that too. You’ll be hearing from us very soon.</p>\n"}]', 0);
SET session_replication_role = DEFAULT;
